Orlovius a hint to the effect that you’ve ceased loving me for years. So let it be the quiet reserved sort of sorrow. Sigh and be silent. Then when you see my corpse, that is, the corpse of a man undistinguishable from me, you’re sure to get a real good shock.”

“Ugh! I can’t, Hermann! I’ll die of fright.”

